Save your time by using a smart extension of Windows Clipboard. Clipà.Vu gives you everything you expect from a classic clipboard manager but it does not stop here… You also get the option to sync and share your clips across all your PCs (available in this giveaway) and mobile devices (available Q3 2017) in a private, secure, and encrypted manner. 
Main features: Optional cloud sync across all your PCs; Optional sync with your Android or iOS devices (Q3 2017); Up to 10.000 history clips, 1.000 favorites, 1.000 images; Advanced search & filtering; Fast switching between rich and plain text; Data encryption;
